terms.title: Beauty
terms.Text: What is produced when GREATNESS fuels GOODNESS

terms.title: Essence
terms.Text: the intrinsic nature or indispensable quality of something, especially something abstract, that determines its character.

terms.title: Excellence
terms.Text: the quality of being outstanding or extremely good. (Being Great at the Good)

terms.title: Goodness
terms.Text: The evaluation of the ESSENCE of our work.

terms.title: Greatness
terms.Text: The evaluation of the QUALITY of our work.
